WEBVTT

00:00.188 --> 00:02.055
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:02.156 --> 00:04.858
Now is the
time of reckoning.

00:06.160 --> 00:08.762
Our task is of vengeance.

00:08.796 --> 00:10.864
But you must know
by now, Cardinal.

00:10.965 --> 00:13.066
Work with us.

00:13.167 --> 00:14.468
Not against us.

00:14.568 --> 00:15.869
We are family!

00:15.970 --> 00:17.037
We are one!

00:17.071 --> 00:19.172
And we will only
triumph as one!

00:25.613 --> 00:28.615
We will have none of that;
you are brothers, after all.

00:28.683 --> 00:30.584
Is His Holiness
lacking something?

00:30.618 --> 00:34.388
Does my presence
no longer fill him with joy?

00:35.990 --> 00:38.292
You're very young, beautiful.

00:38.393 --> 00:42.396
You are more Eve than Adam.

00:42.430 --> 00:46.600
We propose a celebration for
the entire populace of Rome.

00:46.634 --> 00:47.801
Whatever the cost.

00:47.902 --> 00:51.004
Let Rome be full of joy!

00:51.105 --> 00:52.506
I gave my body to you.

00:52.607 --> 00:54.141
I broke my marriage vows.

00:54.208 --> 00:56.310
You bought those three
weeks with murder.

00:56.411 --> 00:58.211
Admit it, Cardinal.

00:58.246 --> 00:59.846
I will search you out.

00:59.914 --> 01:03.250
You may find a nunnery but
you will never be free of me.

01:03.318 --> 01:05.519
Tell me again, my love.
Who was his father?

01:05.620 --> 01:08.021
A groom, Paolo.

01:08.122 --> 01:09.823
Impossible loves;

01:09.924 --> 01:11.959
they can become an addiction.

01:12.026 --> 01:14.928
You fear for the constancy
of your lover's affections?

01:15.029 --> 01:16.229
Don't do as I did.

01:16.331 --> 01:17.931
Allow him his fancy.

01:18.032 --> 01:20.067
Let him look both ways.

01:20.134 --> 01:22.636
But be sure one of those
gazes falls on you.

01:25.873 --> 01:31.548
[♪]

01:31.548 --> 01:35.548
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Borgias 2x02 ♪ </font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Paolo</font>
